{"id":582888,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/我的票圈-今天同性恋封完了吗？-没有/","date":"2018-04-16T01:44:21Z","modified":"2018-04-17T21:56:58Z","title":"我的票圈 | “今天同性恋封完了吗？” “没有”","content":"<p>CDT编辑注：原文已404。</p>\n<p>昨晚的夜，有点格外漫长。</p>\n<p>0 点 53 分，“同志之声”官方微博发布公告宣告将主动「无限期」地停更，任何同志资讯的更新都将暂停。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.45.54-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"479\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.45.54-AM.png 479w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.45.54-AM-300x230.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479px\" /></p>\n<p>截至发文前，这条微博已经拥有了逾3万的转发，其中包括主持人闾丘露薇、电影人程青松。</p>\n<p>在下午四点的时候《好奇心日报》发出了陈莉雅对“同志之声”创始人兼主编花子乐的采访，让我们能更近距离的感受到他们的无奈。（题外话：好奇心日报经常做一些很良心的东西，很佩服。）</p>\n<p>“同志之声”之所以能在10年间在同性恋社群中积攒了如此大的影响力，部分是得益于新浪微博给予的合作（比如：蓝V认证）。但在微博清理公告发出前夕，微博团队中某个支持“同志之声”的高管主动致电，希望后者能够暂停更新。</p>\n<p>谁想逃跑，可背后就是深渊。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_582890\" style=\"width: 509px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.46.47-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"218\" class=\"size-full wp-image-582890\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.46.47-AM.png 499w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.46.47-AM-300x131.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">《你好渣浪，我是同性恋》的文章留言</p></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.22-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"349\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582891\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.22-AM.png 518w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.22-AM-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" /></p>\n<p>我昨天发出的文章在发出后不到12个小时便404了，意料之中。</p>\n<p>在这12个小时内，包括臧鸿飞、耿乐、陈咏开等人转载了这篇文章。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.57-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"254\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582892\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.57-AM.png 580w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.47.57-AM-300x131.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.48.20-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"329\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582893\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.48.20-AM.png 329w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.48.20-AM-206x300.png 206w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" /></p>\n<p>12个小时，109万阅读量，5万个赞，微博转发超过7万。</p>\n<p>我认为这是109万个人在默默关注者这件事，</p>\n<p>至少5万个微信号反对微博对同性恋的封杀，</p>\n<p>超过7万个微博账号用实际行动告诉身边的人：</p>\n<p>“我拒绝沉默，我很骄傲。”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.49.08-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"574\" height=\"185\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582894\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.49.08-AM.png 574w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.49.08-AM-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\" /></p>\n<p>在这12个小时内，更多的人站了出来。</p>\n<p>连夜在话题 #我是同性恋# 下，纷纷现身说法，发出自己的声音。</p>\n<p>以下微博截图均已获得原博主授权</p>\n<p>@以陌叔叔 </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.50.59-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"519\" height=\"345\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582895\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.50.59-AM.png 519w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.50.59-AM-300x199.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.50.59-AM-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 519px) 100vw, 519px\" /></p>\n<p>@竹顶针</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.51.34-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"554\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582896\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.51.34-AM.png 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.51.34-AM-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></p>\n<p>@夏树</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.52.02-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"488\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582897\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.52.02-AM.png 488w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.52.02-AM-293x300.png 293w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.52.02-AM-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 488px) 100vw, 488px\" /></p>\n<p>@澜也_</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.53.07-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"348\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582898\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.53.07-AM.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.53.07-AM-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>@陳振森森</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.53.44-AM.png\" 