inadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.22-AM.png 556w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.22-AM-300x183.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.22-AM-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" /></p>\n<p>@灰嘴入海口</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.44-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"566\" height=\"290\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582904\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.44-AM.png 566w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.55.44-AM-300x154.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" /></p>\n<p>@Naomi_XLT</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.08-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582905\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.08-AM.png 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.08-AM-300x258.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></p>\n<p>@赵为御</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.38-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"383\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582906\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.38-AM.png 564w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-7.56.38-AM-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" /></p>\n<p>@陈咏开的微博在此</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.00.19-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"566\" height=\"283\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582907\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.00.19-AM.png 566w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.00.19-AM-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" /></p>\n<p>@八百伊万礼</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.01.22-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"421\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582908\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.01.22-AM.png 557w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.01.22-AM-300x227.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 557px) 100vw, 557px\" /></p>\n<p>下午 4 点 20 分左右，话题#我是同性恋# 带着无数故事，已经遭到了删除，最终累积阅读量停留在<strong> 2.4 亿</strong>。</p>\n<p>这个数量是我第一次能够切身体会到的声量。</p>\n<p>震撼到我的不是冰冷的数据，而是数字背后每一个勇敢站出来的人。</p>\n<p>谢谢你们。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.08-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" height=\"518\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582909\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.08-AM.png 564w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.08-AM-300x276.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" /></p>\n<p>以前觉得「就算再小，也要呐喊」。</p>\n<p>而现在，我终于感觉不再是一个人了。</p>\n<p>愿微弱的星辰最后汇聚成庞大的星河。</p>\n<p>原每个同性恋都能够真实而自由的活着。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.47-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"576\" height=\"382\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-582910\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.47-AM.png 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.47-AM-300x199.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/Screen-Shot-2018-04-15-at-8.02.47-AM-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" /></p>\n<p>如果爱一个人有罪，就判决我罪该万死。</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[26449,33015,12521,24698,34354,8859,34396,34373]}